Arcadia.KBEH: KBEH, virtual channel 63 (UHF digital channel 42), is a television station serving Los Angeles, California, United States. Licensed to Garden Grove, the station currently airs paid programming. KBEH is owned by Meruelo Broadcasting as part of a duopoly with Los Angeles-licensed Spanish-language independent station KWHY-TV (channel 22); the two stations share channel 42 under a channel sharing agreement.
